on Gas\nsecond-order asymptotic term.\n  We also show that on the whole range $s\\in(0,d)$, the Uniform Electron Gas\nsecond-order constant is continuous in $s$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Jul 2017 17:53:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 Aug 2017 15:58:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 20 Sep 2017 10:35:45 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 11 Sep 2018 22:27:45 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sun, 31 Mar 2019 20:57:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-02"}
