ive functions developed earlier by the first\nauthor and Szemeredi's theorem for long arithmetic progressions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Jul 2017 05:41:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Jan 2018 14:59:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-11"}
