o allow for stimulated\nRaman scattering, which we address up to saturation by accounting for plasma\ninhomogeneity and non-stationarity, nonlinear kinetic effects, and interspeckle\ncoupling.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Jul 2017 07:55:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 15 Sep 2017 13:13:33 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 6 Nov 2017 09:54:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-06"}
