he von Neumann\nTheil index can be generalized by considering the R\\'enyi entropy. We then show\nthat this generalization can be used to bound the negative logarithm of the\ngraph's Jain fairness index.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Jul 2017 10:42:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 Jul 2017 10:13:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 2 Aug 2017 14:45:06 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 3 Feb 2018 10:08:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-06"}
